data.description: Step into your very own ranch cowboy oasis.  This stunning 4 bedroom 2 bathroom is perfect for accommodating your family and guests.  This unique property speaks out a distinctive style of classic ambiance of warmth and adventure.  Situated on a lot of almost 18,000 square feet, this property offers ample space for outdoor entertainment and relaxation.  Beyond the pool and patio which is spacious enough for an ideal outdoor dining, there is spacious bar area for hosting gatherings. Additionally discover a charming cabin room that adds rustic charm to the home. Not to leave out your very own private fish pond oasis.  Bring your own fishes and watch as they gracefully navigate adding a touch of natural beauty to your outdoor haven. Also not to leave out that there are fruit trees, including lemon, orange, peach, and pomegranate, and more, offering a delicious harvest all year round.  With so many charms, the outside ambiance makes you feel serene with ranch setting, perfect for those who love a taste of the wild west in their backyard.  Additional features include quartz kitchen countertops with its unique blend of comfort and adventure this property gives your one of a kind experience. Welcome home your own cowboy retreat.
